				"id": "m1_22",
				"text": "<table><tbody><tr><td><div class=\"tableLine\"><strong>Läkemedel</strong></div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\"><strong>Låg dos<span class=\"tab\"></span><span class=\"tab\"></span></strong></div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\"><strong>Medelhög dos<span class=\"tab\"></span></strong></div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\"><strong>Hög dos</strong></div></td></tr><tr><td><div class=\"tableLine\"><a class=\"index\" id=\"1030571\" data-text=\"beklometason:astma\"></a>Beklometason</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">200–500</div></td><td><p><span class=\"tabstop\"></span><div class=\"tableLine\"><span class=\"tab\"></span>&gt;&nbsp;500–1&nbsp;000</div></p></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">&gt;&nbsp;1&nbsp;000 </div></td></tr><tr><td><div class=\"tableLine\"><a class=\"index\" id=\"1030580\" data-text=\"budesonid:astma\"></a>Budesonid</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">200–400</div></td><td><p><span class=\"tabstop\"></span><div class=\"tableLine\"><span class=\"tab\"></span>&gt;&nbsp;400–800</div></p></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">&gt;&nbsp;800</div></td></tr><tr><td><div class=\"tableLine\"><a class=\"index\" id=\"1030589\" data-text=\"flutikason:astma\"></a>Flutikasonpropionat</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">100–250</div></td><td><p><span class=\"tabstop\"></span><div class=\"tableLine\"><span class=\"tab\"></span>&gt;&nbsp;250–500</div></p></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">&gt;&nbsp;500</div></td></tr><tr><td><div class=\"tableLine\"><a class=\"index\" id=\"1030598\" data-text=\"mometason\"></a>Mometasonfuroat</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">200</div></td><td><p><span class=\"tabstop\"></span><div class=\"tableLine\"><span class=\"tab\"></span>400–800</div></p></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">&gt;&nbsp;800</div></td></tr></tbody></table>"
